Job Description
Responsibilities:In- depth understanding of the specific client product, multiple technologies and alternatives in relevant domainExperience in functional design and fitment analysis of Salesforce.com in large enterpriseLead team of functional consultants offshoreShould have minimum 5 to 7 years of experience in Salesforce.com implementationsVery good Communication and Articulation skillsGood team leadership skillsExperience in multiple CRM package implementations in overall IT experienceExperience in Global Delivery Model working with Offshore teamsEnd to End ownership of complex Salesforce.com projects including deployment and post deployment supportInvolved in:Problem DefinitionArchitectureDiagnostic / Discovery/ As Is AssessmentSolution Evaluation and RecommendationProduct/ Solution DevelopmentDesignTechnology Details:Certified Salesforce Consultant on both sales cloud and service cloud [mandatory]Experience in Presales and solutions [Mandatory]Understanding of P&L parameters required for the successful execution of a Program
